{"title_page": "2001\u201302 EHF Champions League", "text_new": "{{Infobox sport tournament\n| name = [[EHF Champions League]]\n| year = 2001\u201302\n| image =\n| caption = \n| sport = [[Handball]]\n| location =\n| start_date =\n| end_date =\n| administrator =\n| tournament_format =\n| host =\n| venues =\n| participants =\n| purse =\n| champions = [[SC Magdeburg]]\n| matches =\n| previous = [[2000\u201301 EHF Champions League|2000\u201301]]\n| next = [[2002\u201303 EHF Champions League|2002\u201303]]\n}}\nThe '''2001\u201302 [[EHF Champions League]]''' was the 42nd edition of [[Europe]]'s premier club [[Team handball|handball]] tournament.\n\n==Group stage==\n\n=== Group A ===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|winpoints=2\n|show_positions=n\n\n|team1=KOL|name_KOL={{flagicon|DEN}} [[Kolding IF]]\n|team2=SSA|name_SSA={{flagicon|ESP}} [[SDC San Antonio]]\n|team3=SPO|name_SPO={{flagicon|POR}} [[Sporting Clube de Portugal (handball)|Sporting CP]]\n|team4=LOC|name_LOC={{flagicon|Serbia and Montenegro}} [[Lovcen Osiguranje Cetinje]]\n|win_KOL=4|draw_KOL=1|loss_KOL=1|gf_KOL=159|ga_KOL=141\n|win_SSA=4|draw_SSA=1|loss_SSA=1|gf_SSA=188|ga_SSA=152\n|win_SPO=2|draw_SPO=0|loss_SPO=4|gf_SPO=132|ga_SPO=149\n|win_LOC=1|draw_LOC=0|loss_LOC=5|gf_LOC=110|ga_LOC=147\n\n|col_A=green1|text_A=\n|result1=A|result2=A\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n\n===Group B===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=Q\n|winpoints=2\n|show_positions=n\n\n|team1=JAM|name_JAM={{flagicon|CRO}} [[RK Metkovic Jambo]]\n|team2=RED|name_RED={{flagicon|SWE}} [[Redbergslids IK]]\n|team3=SAN|name_SAN={{flagicon|DEN}} [[Sandefjord TIF]]\n|team4=HAP|name_HAP={{flagicon|ISR}} [[Hapoel Rishon LeZion (handball)|Hapoel Rishon LeZion]]\n|win_JAM=5|draw_JAM=0|loss_JAM=1|gf_JAM=166|ga_JAM=138\n|win_RED=5|draw_RED=0|loss_RED=1|gf_RED=167|ga_RED=151\n|win_SAN=2|draw_SAN=0|loss_SAN=4|gf_SAN=161|ga_SAN=164\n|win_HAP=0|draw_HAP=0|loss_HAP=6|gf_HAP=151|ga_HAP=192\n\n|col_A=green1|text_A=\n